<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>손경제 Daily Brief — {{ date_kr }}</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable-dynamic-subset.min.css">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #FFFDF5;
  --card-bg: #FFFFFF;
  --border: #F0E8D8;
  --text: #2D2A26;
  --text-dim: rgba(45, 42, 38, 0.65);
  --up: #E55C20;
  --down: #3B82F6;
  --flat: #888;
  --shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; }
html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body {
  font-family: 'Pretendard Variable', Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-weight: 400;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}
.num { font-family: 'DM Sans', 'Pretendard Variable', sans-serif; font-feature-settings: 'tnum'; }

.container { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 16px 60px; }

/* Header */
.header {
  position: relative;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF3D0 0%, #FFE8A3 50%, #FFD97A 100%);
  padding: 40px 32px 36px;
  border-radius: 0 0 24px 24px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  overflow: hidden;
  max-width: 720px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}
.header__date { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(45,42,38,0.7); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.header__title { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 8px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
.header__subtitle { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(45,42,38,0.7); font-weight: 500; margin: 0; }
.header__rabbit {
  position: absolute;
  right: 24px;
  bottom: 16px;
  font-size: 64px;
  opacity: 0.25;
  line-height: 1;
  user-select: none;
}

/* Section header / Badge */
.badge {
  display: inline-block;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFE8A3 0%, #FF9800 100%);
  color: #FFFFFF;
  padding: 10px 22px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 700;
  box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(255,152,0,0.3);
}
.section-center { text-align: center; margin: 32px 0 18px; }
.section-h2 {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin: 36px 0 14px;
  letter-spacing: -0.3px;
}

/* Episode */
.episode {
  background: var(--card-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 18px 22px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}
.episode__label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.episode__title { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 10px; }
.episode__audio audio { width: 100%; margin-top: 8px; }

/* Indicator */
.ind-group { margin-bottom: 12px; }
.ind-group__label {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 14px 0 8px;
  padding-left: 4px;
}
.ind-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
  gap: 10px;
}
.ind {
  background: var(--card-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 14px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}
.ind__name { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 6px; font-weight: 500; }
.ind__value { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; }
.ind__change { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 2px; }
.ind__change.up { color: var(--up); }
.ind__change.down { color: var(--down); }
.ind__change.flat { color: var(--flat); }

/* Policy bar */
.policy {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF8E1 0%, #FFE8A3 100%);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 16px 18px;
  margin-top: 14px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}
.policy__item { text-align: center; }
.policy__label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 4px; font-weight: 500; }
.policy__value { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; }
.policy__outlook { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 2px; }

/* News card */
.card {
  background: var(--card-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 20px 22px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}
.card__title { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.4; }
.card__summary { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text); margin: 0 0 12px; }
.card__why { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); padding: 12px 14px; background: #FFFAEB; border-left: 3px solid #FFD97A; border-radius: 8px; margin: 12px 0; }
.card__why-label { font-weight: 700; margin-right: 4px; }
.card__points { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); padding-left: 22px; margin: 8px 0; }
.card__points li { margin-bottom: 4px; }
.card__sources { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 12px; }
.card__sources a { color: #3B82F6; text-decoration: none; }
.card__sources a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

/* Friendly economics */
.friendly {
  background: var(--card-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 22px 24px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}
.friendly__topic { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 12px; line-height: 1.4; }
.friendly__explanation { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 16px; }
.cmp-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 12px; }
.cmp-table th { background: #FFF3D0; padding: 10px; text-align: left; font-weight: 700; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.cmp-table td { padding: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--border); vertical-align: top; }
.cmp-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #FFFDF5; }

/* Rabbit idea */
.idea {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFFAEB 0%, #FFF3D0 100%);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 20px 22px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}
.idea__format { display: inline-block; background: var(--text); color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 12px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
.idea__hook { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 10px; line-height: 1.4; }
.idea__target { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); margin: 0 0 10px; }
.idea__outline { font-size: 14px; padding-left: 22px; margin: 0; }
.idea__outline li { margin-bottom: 4px; }

/* Footer bar */
.footer-bar {
  height: 10px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FFEB3B 0%, #FF9800 50%, #FF5722 100%);
  margin-top: 40px;
}
.footer-note { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); padding: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .header__title { font-size: 22px; }
  .header__rabbit { font-size: 48px; right: 16px; }
  .ind__value { font-size: 19px; }
  .card, .friendly, .idea { padding: 16px 18px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="header">
  <div class="header__date">{{ date_kr }}</div>
  <h1 class="header__title">손경제 Daily Brief</h1>
  <p class="header__subtitle">햇님이들을 위한 오늘의 경제 한 입 🌞</p>
  <div class="header__rabbit">🐰</div>
</header>

<main class="container">

  {% if episode %}
  <div class="episode">
    <div class="episode__label">📻 오늘의 손경제</div>
    <div class="episode__title">{{ episode.title }}</div>
    {% if episode.audio_url %}
    <audio controls preload="none" src="{{ episode.audio_url }}"></audio>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <div class="section-center">
    <span class="badge">📊 오늘의 경제지표 한눈에 보기!</span>
  </div>

  {% if indicators and indicators.domestic %}
  <div class="ind-group">
    <div class="ind-group__label">🇰🇷 국내</div>
    <div class="ind-grid">
      {% for ind in indicators.domestic %}
      <div class="ind">
        <div class="ind__name">{{ ind.name }}</div>
        <div class="ind__value num">{{ ind.value | fmt_value(ind.unit) }}</div>
        <div class="ind__change {{ ind.direction }} num">
          {% if ind.direction == 'up' %}▲{% elif ind.direction == 'down' %}▼{% else %}―{% endif %}
          {{ ind.change | fmt_abs(ind.unit) }} ({{ ind.change_pct | fmt_pct }})
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {% if indicators and indicators.world %}
  <div class="ind-group">
    <div class="ind-group__label">🌎 글로벌</div>
    <div class="ind-grid">
      {% for ind in indicators.world %}
      <div class="ind">
        <div class="ind__name">{{ ind.name }}</div>
        <div class="ind__value num">{{ ind.value | fmt_value(ind.unit) }}</div>
        <div class="ind__change {{ ind.direction }} num">
          {% if ind.direction == 'up' %}▲{% elif ind.direction == 'down' %}▼{% else %}―{% endif %}
          {{ ind.change | fmt_abs(ind.unit) }} ({{ ind.change_pct | fmt_pct }})
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {% if policy_rates %}
  <div class="policy">
    <div class="policy__item">
      <div class="policy__label">🇰🇷 한국 기준금리</div>
      <div class="policy__value num">{{ policy_rates.korea.value }}%</div>
      <div class="policy__outlook">{{ policy_rates.korea.outlook }}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="policy__item">
      <div class="policy__label">🇺🇸 미국 기준금리</div>
      <div class="policy__value num">{{ policy_rates.us.value }}%</div>
      <div class="policy__outlook">{{ policy_rates.us.outlook }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {% if news_cards %}
  <h2 class="section-h2">📰 오늘의 뉴스 카드</h2>
  {% for n in news_cards %}
  <article class="card">
    <h3 class="card__title">{{ n.title }}</h3>
    <p class="card__summary">{{ n.summary }}</p>
    {% if n.why_it_matters %}
    <div class="card__why">
      <span class="card__why-label">🔍 직장인이 알아야 하는 이유</span>
      {{ n.why_it_matters }}
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if n.key_points %}
    <ul class="card__points">
      {% for p in n.key_points %}<li>{{ p }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% endif %}
    {% if n.sources %}
    <div class="card__sources">
      출처:
      {% for s in n.sources %}<a href="{{ s.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ s.title }}</a>{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
  {% endif %}

  {% if friendly_economics %}
  <h2 class="section-h2">💡 친절한 경제</h2>
  <div class="friendly">
    <h3 class="friendly__topic">{{ friendly_economics.topic }}</h3>
    <p class="friendly__explanation">{{ friendly_economics.explanation }}</p>
    {% if friendly_economics.comparison_table and friendly_economics.comparison_table.rows %}
    <table class="cmp-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>{% for h in friendly_economics.comparison_table.headers %}<th>{{ h }}</th>{% endfor %}</tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for row in friendly_economics.comparison_table.rows %}
        <tr>{% for cell in row %}<td>{{ cell }}</td>{% endfor %}</tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {% if rabbithat_ideas %}
  <h2 class="section-h2">🐰 래빗해빛 콘텐츠 소재</h2>
  {% for idea in rabbithat_ideas %}
  <div class="idea">
    <span class="idea__format">{{ idea.format }}</span>
    <h3 class="idea__hook">{{ idea.hook }}</h3>
    {% if idea.target_audience %}<p class="idea__target">🎯 타깃: {{ idea.target_audience }}</p>{% endif %}
    {% if idea.outline %}
    <ol class="idea__outline">
      {% for line in idea.outline %}<li>{{ line }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ol>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
  {% endif %}

</main>

<div class="footer-bar"></div>
<div class="footer-note">
  생성 시각: {{ generated_at }} · Claude로 자동 생성됨<br>
  손경제(MBC) 콘텐츠는 MBC 저작권을 따릅니다 · 본 페이지는 학습·참고 목적
</div>

</body>
</html>
